headline: TKO Holdings (TKO): Top Positive Contributor to Cooper Investors Global Equities Fund’s 12-Month Returns
summary: Cooper Investors, an investment management firm, released its “Cooper Investors Global Equities Fund (Unhedged)” third-quarter 2025 investor letter. A copy of the letter can be downloaded here. The fund returned -0.04% in the third quarter, compared to a 6.42% return for the MSCI AC World Index Net Divs in Australian Dollars.
